        "subject": "LU-6194 tests: Skip sanity 162c for MDS older than 2.6.92",
        "message": "LU-6194 tests: Skip sanity 162c for MDS older than 2.6.92\n\nSanity test 162c tests that a path can have more than 100\nsubdirectories. The limit of only 100 subdirectories in a\npath was removed by a patch for LU-4239 and landed in Lustre\nmaster tag 2.6.92.\n\nSkip sanity test 162c for MDSs with version less than 2.6.92.\n\nTest-Parameters: alwaysuploadlogs envdefinitions=ONLY=162c \\ \nclientdistro=el6.6 mdsdistro=el6.6 ossdistro=el6.6 clientarch=x86_64 \\\nmdsarch=x86_64 ossarch=x86_64 clientjob=lustre-b2_6 mdsjob=lustre-b2_6 \\\nossjob=lustre-b2_6 clientbuildno=19 mdsbuildno=19 ossbuildno=19 \\\ntestlist=sanity \n\nSigned-off-by: James Nunez <james.a.nunez@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I326639bf45c77c4600c9ca61ab34878bd8009070"
      },
